 A Nigerian evangelist took to social media to warn men and women from making trending hairstyles that would lead them to hellfire. According to her, wearing wigs; using weavons, relaxers, hair gels and even having haircuts as a lady, are sins that will lead one to hell. Admonishing her audience, the self-assured evangelist called on people to repent because the hairstyles and the hair routines she listed are from the satanic world. Watch The Video Below;   A post shared by Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) 